Form validation using hibernate validator

1.configure dynamic web project to maven
2.dependencies in pom.xml
3.Student.java class
4.BindingResult will check targeted object for form validation error.
5.WebConfig : configure viewResolver, message.properties and LocalValidatorFactoryBean 
configure LocalValidatorFactoryBean in webAppConfig because bindingResult need validator(LocalValidatorFactoryBean).
*LocalValidatorFactoryBean implements both javax.validation.Validator* and org.springframework.validation.Validator. 
6.webAppInitializer(container configuration) : webappconfig
7.studenForm with error tags
